<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM9.9">
<l>kōṅkala rumpoḻil māliruñ cōlaiyil koṉṟaikaḷmēl</l>
<l>tūṅkupoṉ mālaika ḷōṭuṭa ṉāyniṉṟu tūṅkukiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>pūṅkoḷ tirumukat tumaṭut tūtiya caṅkoliyum</l>
<l>cārṅkavil nāṇoli yuntalaip peyvateñ ñāṉṟukolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I tarry staying along with the golden garlands that hang</l>
<l>upon the laburnum trees in Māliruñcōlai with blossoming Caung-trees groves.</l>
<l>On which day will the sound of the conch—which [He] blew by placing [it]</l>
<l>on [His] beautiful, sacred lips—and the sound of the Śārṅga bowstring approach?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
